OL,3,CMeet Steve Jarvis: The dad who lost
OL,4,Chis sight but not his passion for
OL,5,Cfootball
OL,7,FA football fan who lost his sight in a
OL,8,Fmotorbike accident says he never even
OL,9,Fthought about stopping going to
OL,10,Fmatches to support his team.
OL,12,FSteve Jarvis from Salisbury may be
OL,13,Fblind but his passion for Southampton
OL,14,Ffootball club - along with his son's
OL,15,Fhelping hand - means he travels to
OL,16,Fsupport The Saints home and away.
OL,18,FSteve was in a coma for 71 days
OL,19,Ffollowing a motorbike accident in
OL,20,FBournemouth.
