OL,3,CMeet Steve Jarvis: The dad who lost
OL,4,Chis sight but not his passion for
OL,5,Cfootball
OL,7,FBut within 6 months he was back
OL,8,Fsupporting his team.
OL,10,FAs the years have gone by, he and his
OL,11,Fson, Dan, have travelled across
OL,12,FEngland and Europe to cheer on The
OL,13,FSaints.
OL,15,FHe's always been a huge Southampton
OL,16,Ffan and he told ITV News Meridian he
OL,17,Fmay have lost his sight but never his
OL,18,Fpassion for the football club.
