OL,3,CMeet Steve Jarvis: The dad who lost
OL,4,Chis sight but not his passion for
OL,5,Cfootball
OL,7,FWhen asked if ever thought he'd never
OL,8,Fgo to a Saints game again, Steve said:
OL,9,F"No. I really enjoyed following Saints.
OL,11,F"The atmosphere of the crowd and
OL,12,Feverything. I couldn't shift it. It
OL,13,Fwould stay with me for the rest of my
OL,14,Flife and will continue to do so."
OL,16,FThe father and son say supporting the
OL,17,Fclub home and away has helped develop
OL,18,Fa special bond between the pair.
