OL,3,CMeet Steve Jarvis: The dad who lost
OL,4,Chis sight but not his passion for
OL,5,Cfootball
OL,7,FSteve said: "As a father and son, Dan
OL,8,Fand I are always talking about
OL,9,Ffootball. Not just Saints. We talk
OL,10,Ffootball around the world. But for us
OL,11,Fsaints is best."
OL,13,FDan said "It's brought us closer
OL,14,Ftogether I think. Growing up the
OL,15,Frelationship was a little bit
OL,16,Fdifferent. But coming to games has
OL,17,Falways been special and it always will
OL,18,Fbe."
