OL,3,CMeet Steve Jarvis: The dad who lost
OL,4,Chis sight but not his passion for
OL,5,Cfootball
OL,7,FOn occasion, Dan has had to provide
OL,8,Fcommentary for his Dad. But when
OL,9,Fthey're at St Mary's, a Special Audio
OL,10,FDescription Service is available.
OL,12,FHelen Goosey, Disability liaison
OL,13,Fofficer, Southampton FC said: "It's a
OL,14,Fmuch better experience for supporters
OL,15,Fbecause they feel more included, the
OL,16,Fsame as any other supporter would
OL,17,Fwithin the ground and that's the whole
OL,18,Fpoint that every supporter has the
OL,19,Fsame experience."
