OL,3,CMeet Steve Jarvis: The dad who lost
OL,4,Chis sight but not his passion for
OL,5,Cfootball
OL,7,FSteve said: "It's almost like I can
OL,8,Fsee the game.
OL,10,F"You know exactly what's happening as
OL,11,Fthe ball's passed, who's got it and
OL,12,Fthe blindness doesn't come in to it
OL,13,Fbecause it's there at my ears."
OL,15,FSteve and Dan say there have been many
OL,16,Fhighlights from supporting Southampton
OL,17,Fover the years and they're hoping for
OL,18,Fanother on Friday night (17 May) when
OL,19,Ftheir idols take on West Brom in the
OL,20,FPlay-Off Semi Finals at St Mary's.
